CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 5, 1961, pg. A15, reads: "FROGS' Teen Queen - Morris Fountain, chairman for the Frogs' teen-age dance, places a crown of flowers on the head of Marguerite Peters, center, who was named 'Queen' of the affair. Other lovely contestants are, left to right: Yvonne Rickmond, Rosalyn King. Marilyn Cobb, Gretel Cobb and Diana Fountain. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Yvonne Rickmond, Rosalyn King, Morris Fountain placing crown on head of Marguerite Peters, Marilyn Cobb, Gretel Cobb and Diana Fountain posed in Loendi Club for FROGS club teen dance
